{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"7":{"eng-name":"Fasting","ara-name":"كتاب الصيام"}},"section_detail":{"7":{"hadithnumber_first":1638,"hadithnumber_last":1782,"arabicnumber_first":1638,"arabicnumber_last":1782}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1739,"arabicnumber":1739,"text":"It was narrated from Rabi’ah bin Ghaz that he asked ‘Aishah about the fasting of the Messenger of Allah (ﷺ). She said:“He used to make sure he fasted on Mondays and Thursdays.”","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":7,"hadith":102},"chapter":{"id":42,"ara-name":"باب صِيَامِ يَوْمِ الاِثْنَيْنِ وَالْخَمِيسِ","eng-name":"Fasting on Mondays and Thursdays","isFirstHadith":true}}]}